messages.messageBody:
Hello everyone. I just wanted to touch base with everyone to let them
know That if you signed up for the Valentine exchange, it will be
mailed out soon. I have had to work 16 hr. days the last 3 days and
have ended up ill now. The response was over 600 children on the list
and I am the only one to put into groups by age and states then cut
them into groups of 30 and then email each group to each person in the
group. So it is alot of work and I will be working on them and
hopefully get them out this week. Please bear with me in this.
Thanks,
Pebs
